41:28.653 --> 41:31.623
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

41:33.199 --> 41:37.579
- Laszlo, can you show me where they are?
- But they'll kill you.

41:37.662 --> 41:40.666
If I don't stop them,
they'll kill everyone.

41:46.587 --> 41:48.214
Then follow me.

41:51.843 --> 41:55.188
- What are they keeping us here for?
- I don't know.

41:55.263 --> 41:57.263
Got a nasty feeling we're being
kept in the larder.

42:02.854 --> 42:05.107
What are they doing? What's wrong?
What's wrong?

42:05.189 --> 42:08.159
Silence! Silence!

42:09.777 --> 42:11.654
What the hell is that?

42:14.282 --> 42:17.786
You will form a line! Move! Move!

42:17.952 --> 42:20.501
Just do what it says, everyone, okay?
Just obey.

42:20.580 --> 42:24.960
The female is wise. Obey!

42:25.084 --> 42:29.055
- Report!
- These are strong specimens.

42:29.130 --> 42:31.633
They will help the Dalek cause.

42:31.799 --> 42:32.846
Dale k.

42:32.925 --> 42:36.646
What is the status
